question: Where can I find café as you head towards Hudson Gateway Place LLC, San Jose, CA from the View Lounge, San Francisco, CA, within a radius of 80 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.404326 37.785414)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-121.923427 37.369617)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'cafe'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.404326 37.785414)',4326)::geography, 80000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-122.404326 37.785414)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
